reviewText: Garbage. Steves work, as we all know by now, is fraud. No one will get rich. Steve is Georgia swamp poor. His goal is to sell poorly written books with the vocabulary of a 4th grader.

The author has put extra efforts in creating such a masterpiece. The quality of material of this DVD is worth more than its price. Easy to understand content for everyone. From me, I will definitely rate this book and the author's efforts a 5-STAR. I highly recommend this book to everyone.
